name: KLM 777-206ER [PH-BQE] Loud Takeoff From Calgary (New Runway) ᴴᴰ
description:
NEW INTRO! Tell me what you guys think :D
Here we have KLM 678 departing Calgary International Airport's new runway, going to Amsterdam. Just listen to those GE-90s!  Don't expect any other videos from here, however. There were lots of "No Trespassing" signs which I only noticed on my way out :P Hope you guys enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
